ygData.messageBody:
Sorry to say that while you look cool, Harmonic looks much cooler in black.
As a wood elf dressed in all black you look more like your about to say
"now's the time on sprockets when we dance" than "I'm Batman" ;-)

I'm teasing you...

Time for the 50 questions game:

What is the glowing red thing in your left hand and what are the stats and
where did it come from?

I have seen them around now and then I was curious what they are.

-Faras
